mgui.interfaces.projects

Class ProjectInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • mgui.interfaces.AbstractInterfaceObject
      • mgui.interfaces.projects.ProjectInstance
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<ProjectInstance>, AttributeListener, InterfaceObject, NamedObject, TreeObject, CleanableObject, XMLObject, IconObject

    public class ProjectInstance
extends AbstractInterfaceObject
implements IconObject, AttributeListener, java.lang.Comparable<ProjectInstance>, XMLObject
    Specifies an element instance in a project (e.g., a subject). The instance can be minimally specified by a name and a type, but other implementations can expand its attributes.
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Andrew Reid
